83-174.05.Violation of conditions of community supervision; penalty.

Failure to comply with the conditions of community supervision imposed by the department is a Class IV felony for the first offense and a Class III felony for any subsequent offense.

SourceLaws 2006, LB 1199, § 91;Laws 2018, LB841, § 19;Laws 2025, LB150, § 138.Operative Date: September 3, 2025
